1
00:00:06,016 --> 00:00:09,472
(Celestial Duchy)

2
00:00:09,472 --> 00:00:12,096
(1999)

3
00:00:12,096 --> 00:00:15,104
(Changqingtai City)

4
00:00:15,279 --> 00:00:16,679
(Here's a breaking story.)

5
00:00:16,679 --> 00:00:19,359
(Deep In The Bustle
in the heart of Chinatown)

6
00:00:19,359 --> 00:00:21,199
(is now renowned far and wide.)

7
00:00:21,199 --> 00:00:22,879
(Although newly established,)

8
00:00:22,879 --> 00:00:25,399
(Tu Jiasheng, Nie Feng, Zhao Lu)
(backed by the powerful connections)

9
00:00:25,399 --> 00:00:26,320
(Deep In The Bustle)
(of its three founders,)

10
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,559
(it rapidly claimed)

11
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:30,600
(the top spot
in the city's entertainment industry.)

12
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:32,320
(But now, with the key founder)

13
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,600
(Nie Feng's father)

14
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,280
(Anti-corruption Investigation Team)
(caught in a political storm,)

15
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,399
(the future of Deep In The Bustle
may be at risk.)

16
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:38,000
(After all,)

17
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,320
(a business this profitable)

18
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:41,520
(attracts many greedy eyes.)

19
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,799
(It's said that Chief Phachai)

20
00:00:43,799 --> 00:00:45,399
(has publicly declared more than once)

21
00:00:45,399 --> 00:00:47,039
(to take over Deep In The Bustle.)

22
00:00:47,159 --> 00:00:48,399
(How this will end)

23
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:49,520
(remains to be seen.)

24
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:51,680
(Chinatown)

25
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:06,920
(Welcome to Deep In The Bustle.)

26
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:26,480
Congratulations to Director Jimiya
for taking two beauties.

27
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,239
Next, let's welcome

28
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:30,879
the chief of Changqingtai City Police,

29
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,280
Phachai

30
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:35,000
to the Losha Pavilion.

31
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,280
At Losha Pavilion,

32
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,599
each token costs 100,000.

33
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,760
The girls whose tokens are taken

34
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,640
tonight

35
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:46,120
belong to Chief Phachai.

36
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:56,840
Chief Phachai is spending big tonight.

37
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,040
Looks like he is taking

38
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,519
all the beauties home!

39
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,319
Congratulations to Chief Phachai

40
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:04,120
for winning a bevy of beauties.

41
00:02:10,304 --> 00:02:12,768
=The Glory Fades=

42
00:02:13,312 --> 00:02:15,471
=Episode 1=
(No Causing Trouble, But Not Afraid of It)

43
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,759
Is this a scam?

44
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:19,719
(Qin Wei, GM of Deep In The Bustle)
I prepaid 500,000 dollars as a deposit,

45
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,599
and you tell me it's not enough?

46
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:24,199
Chief Phachai.

47
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,560
The entry fee for Losha Pavilion,

48
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,560
top beauties' chamber,
is 188,000 per person.

49
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:31,759
(Phachai, Police Chief)
You flipped eleven tokens tonight.

50
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:33,599
That totals 1.1 million.

51
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,759
Our prices

52
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,680
are clearly marked.

53
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,199
Refund me!

54
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,599
Wipe the bill!

55
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,719
Let me tell you.

56
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:55,759
I can shut this place down right now
on prostitution charges.

57
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,599
Chief Phachai.

58
00:02:59,424 --> 00:03:00,560
That would be

59
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,600
against the rules.

60
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,760
Qin Wei.

61
00:03:03,441 --> 00:03:05,281
I make the rules here.

62
00:03:06,961 --> 00:03:08,241
Your Fifth Brother Tu Jiasheng

63
00:03:08,241 --> 00:03:09,520
is nothing!

64
00:03:09,881 --> 00:03:11,241
He's just a puppet.

65
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,121
And your Sixth Brother,

66
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,080
Zhao Lu.

67
00:03:14,961 --> 00:03:17,281
What's the use
of having a government official father?

68
00:03:18,161 --> 00:03:19,681
I'm the same rank as him!

69
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:23,800
He still relies on Governor Nie
to cover for him.

70
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,640
Now everyone knows

71
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:26,640
the Nie family

72
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,760
is hanging by a thread.

73
00:03:31,161 --> 00:03:32,480
Where are the three brothers now?

74
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,001
Which one of you

75
00:03:37,161 --> 00:03:38,800
dares talk to me?

76
00:03:39,584 --> 00:03:42,592
(Tu Jiasheng,
Founder of Deep In The Bustle)

77
00:03:44,401 --> 00:03:45,721
I'm letting you stay open.

78
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,161
I'm already doing you a favor.

79
00:03:49,001 --> 00:03:50,281
Don't push it.

80
00:03:51,961 --> 00:03:52,640
Smash it up!

81
00:03:55,281 --> 00:03:56,681
Hello, Feng.

82
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:58,640
Are you handling this?

83
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,800
Phachai's going crazy.

84
00:03:59,881 --> 00:04:00,760
Lu.

85
00:04:00,881 --> 00:04:02,281
Behave.

86
00:04:02,281 --> 00:04:02,961
(Zhao Lu, Founder of Deep In The Bustle)

87
00:04:02,961 --> 00:04:05,001
Don't you know my family's situation?

88
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,561
Put Jiasheng on.

89
00:04:15,881 --> 00:04:16,960
Hello, Feng.

90
00:04:17,441 --> 00:04:19,960
Tu Jiasheng, are you useless?

91
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,881
Can't you even handle Phachai?

92
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:23,041
I'm telling you.

93
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:25,601
If he wrecks it today,

94
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,441
you'll answer for it.

95
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,640
Do we make a move?

96
00:04:39,601 --> 00:04:40,400
No fatalities.

97
00:04:42,601 --> 00:04:44,280
The thugs he brought are easy.

98
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:46,080
But if he calls men

99
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,681
from the police station,

100
00:04:47,681 --> 00:04:49,160
then what...

101
00:04:49,241 --> 00:04:50,080
I'll handle it.

102
00:05:36,361 --> 00:05:37,400
All officers!

103
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,840
Surround Deep In The Bustle completely.

104
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,840
Not a single fly gets out.

105
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,481
Tu Jiasheng.

106
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,960
If you've got guts, open the door!

107
00:06:50,881 --> 00:06:52,760
Kneel and call me grandpa,

108
00:06:53,441 --> 00:06:55,121
and I might spare your lives.

109
00:06:55,361 --> 00:06:57,001
I want Deep In The Bustle,

110
00:06:57,361 --> 00:06:58,561
not your worthless lives.

111
00:06:58,801 --> 00:06:59,720
Come out!

112
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,041
Come out!

113
00:07:13,388 --> 00:07:14,656
(Grand Princess Manor, Celestial Duchy)

114
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:20,921
Hello?

115
00:07:21,481 --> 00:07:22,441
Your Highness.

116
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,001
What?

117
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,881
I guessed right.

118
00:07:26,361 --> 00:07:28,160
(Grand Princess of Celestial Duchy)
I knew you'd come to me.

119
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,960
(Raja Kalina)
I just didn't expect

120
00:07:30,121 --> 00:07:31,681
it to come so soon.

121
00:07:31,681 --> 00:07:33,121
I'm starting the countdown now.

122
00:07:33,121 --> 00:07:34,121
In thirty minutes,

123
00:07:34,121 --> 00:07:34,921
you three

124
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,681
get out of Deep In The Bustle.

125
00:07:38,561 --> 00:07:39,320
Fine.

126
00:07:39,921 --> 00:07:41,160
In twenty minutes,

127
00:07:41,601 --> 00:07:44,200
my Royal Guards will arrive.

128
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,241
And I'll keep my promise

129
00:07:46,481 --> 00:07:47,640
and break up with Paria.

130
00:07:48,361 --> 00:07:50,881
Remember your promise.

131
00:07:54,041 --> 00:07:54,881
As expected,

132
00:07:56,041 --> 00:07:57,960
my Paria was nothing

133
00:07:58,681 --> 00:08:00,881
more than your stepping stone.

134
00:08:07,681 --> 00:08:09,121
Last ten minutes.

135
00:08:09,441 --> 00:08:11,681
One last chance to live.

136
00:08:12,041 --> 00:08:13,801
All units, stand ready.

137
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,640
Jiasheng.

138
00:08:24,241 --> 00:08:24,928
I've got this.

139
00:08:24,928 --> 00:08:25,640
You should leave.

140
00:08:26,481 --> 00:08:28,080
Nine minutes left.

141
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,200
Open the door.

142
00:09:14,361 --> 00:09:15,601
Chief Phachai.

143
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:19,481
I never expected

144
00:09:20,081 --> 00:09:21,280
the real backbone here

145
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,520
is you, the so-called puppet.

146
00:09:24,481 --> 00:09:26,001
To be used by Nie Feng,

147
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,721
you really have guts.

148
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,280
Come on.

149
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,800
Kneel and beg me.

150
00:09:32,961 --> 00:09:33,881
Being my dog

151
00:09:34,241 --> 00:09:35,520
is much better

152
00:09:36,081 --> 00:09:37,440
than being the Nie family's dog.

153
00:09:38,121 --> 00:09:39,400
Chief Phachai.

154
00:09:39,961 --> 00:09:41,640
You've deployed so many policemen.

155
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:44,081
I should agree to anything.

156
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,881
But just this one thing, I can't.

157
00:09:45,881 --> 00:09:47,040
My knees are bad.

158
00:09:47,241 --> 00:09:48,081
I can't kneel.

159
00:09:49,241 --> 00:09:50,361
Ungrateful!

160
00:09:50,961 --> 00:09:51,680
Get him!

161
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,201
Attention!

162
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,721
We are the Royal Palm Guard.

163
00:10:08,481 --> 00:10:09,841
The Grand Princess commanded

164
00:10:09,841 --> 00:10:11,800
all of you lay down your weapons

165
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,121
and submit.

166
00:10:13,481 --> 00:10:14,160
Repeat.

167
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,121
Lay down your weapons

168
00:10:15,121 --> 00:10:16,481
and submit.

169
00:10:16,961 --> 00:10:17,640
Repeat.

170
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:20,121
Lay down your weapons and submit.

171
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:21,520
No!

172
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,640
Nobody move!

173
00:10:27,201 --> 00:10:28,001
You punk.

174
00:10:29,121 --> 00:10:30,881
You called the Royal Guards?

175
00:10:33,312 --> 00:10:33,875
Darn it!

176
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:34,961
Nobody lives!

177
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:44,001
Feeling better now?

178
00:10:44,241 --> 00:10:45,361
Chief Phachai.

179
00:10:52,361 --> 00:10:53,361
Let me go!

180
00:10:53,680 --> 00:10:54,760
Let me go!

181
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,481
Tu Jiasheng!

182
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,081
Tu Jiasheng!

183
00:10:58,081 --> 00:10:59,081
What's so funny?

184
00:11:03,001 --> 00:11:03,920
You owe me a life.

185
00:11:05,881 --> 00:11:06,680
Alright.

186
00:11:59,001 --> 00:12:01,216
(In the third year
after Deep In The Bustle's founded,)

187
00:12:01,481 --> 00:12:03,040
(used the Grand Princess' power,)

188
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:05,361
(I had Phachai, who intended
to annex Deep In The Bustle,)

189
00:12:05,361 --> 00:12:06,440
(thrown in prison.)

190
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:09,121
(The price was breaking up
with her daughter.)

191
00:12:09,601 --> 00:12:11,160
(Half a year later,)

192
00:12:11,201 --> 00:12:12,760
(I met An Ruoxi.)

193
00:12:13,201 --> 00:12:14,520
(In the two years that followed,)

194
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:17,400
(both my career
and love life flourished.)

195
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:19,001
(However, I didn't know)

196
00:12:19,361 --> 00:12:21,001
(that the thing that'd change my life)

197
00:12:21,081 --> 00:12:23,160
(was already approaching.)

198
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:26,520
(It was Deep In The Bustle's
fifth anniversary)

199
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,160
(when an uninvited guest arrived.)

200
00:12:28,601 --> 00:12:30,601
(Vice leader
of the notorious Yanyue Gang,)

201
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,280
(Huang Weide.)

202
00:12:40,121 --> 00:12:41,081
Hello, Mr. Huang.

203
00:12:41,721 --> 00:12:43,001
It's such a wonderful day.

204
00:12:43,841 --> 00:12:45,881
Mind if I show up uninvited?

205
00:12:48,121 --> 00:12:49,121
Are you...

206
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,680
Call Tu Jiasheng out.

207
00:12:58,481 --> 00:12:59,520
Tu Jiasheng.

208
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:01,640
(Huang Weide,
Vice Leader of Yanyue Gang)

209
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:03,241
Getting arrogant now?

210
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,520
You don't even greet me?

211
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,520
Tu Jiasheng!

212
00:13:14,201 --> 00:13:14,721
Come out!

213
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,800
Tu Jiasheng!

214
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:18,721
Mr. Huang?

215
00:13:18,721 --> 00:13:20,121
(Deep In The Bustle)
Rolling in money now, huh?

216
00:13:20,121 --> 00:13:22,481
- What brings you?
- You dare not come out to greet me?

217
00:13:23,361 --> 00:13:25,121
I didn't know you were coming.

218
00:13:25,121 --> 00:13:25,961
Wei.

219
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:27,760
Arrange a private bath.

220
00:13:27,881 --> 00:13:28,400
Got it.

221
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,481
This way, Mr. Huang.

222
00:13:29,481 --> 00:13:30,400
Private bath?

223
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:33,400
You think I'm that easy to fool?

224
00:13:34,321 --> 00:13:35,001
Mr. Huang.

225
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:37,241
Not just a private bath.

226
00:13:37,241 --> 00:13:38,481
You'll see.

227
00:13:38,920 --> 00:13:39,481
Here, please.

228
00:13:39,481 --> 00:13:40,721
Everything you want is inside.

229
00:13:40,721 --> 00:13:41,400
Jiasheng.

230
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,040
Don't worry.

231
00:13:42,201 --> 00:13:43,800
(An Ruoxi, Tu Jiasheng's fiancée)
I've arranged for the guests over there.

232
00:13:43,881 --> 00:13:44,520
Okay, got it.

233
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:45,121
You go ahead.

234
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:46,880
Wait.

235
00:13:47,881 --> 00:13:48,481
Who's she?

236
00:13:49,601 --> 00:13:50,160
Mr. Huang.

237
00:13:50,721 --> 00:13:51,920
She's our boss' wife.

238
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:52,520
Right.

239
00:13:53,081 --> 00:13:53,881
Your woman?

240
00:13:54,321 --> 00:13:55,920
You lucky man.

241
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:58,040
No wonder you ditched
the Grand Princess' daughter.

242
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,961
I want her tonight.

243
00:13:59,961 --> 00:14:01,361
Mr. Huang.

244
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:02,400
Well.

245
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,400
We have better ones

246
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,241
inside.

247
00:14:04,241 --> 00:14:05,881
I'll arrange for you.

248
00:14:05,881 --> 00:14:06,721
Just go inside.

249
00:14:06,721 --> 00:14:07,400
Rest assured.

250
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:09,560
Come on.

251
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,961
I only want her.

252
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:12,001
Her.

253
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,680
Or I'll shut this place down.

254
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,920
No problem.

255
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:17,520
I'll change and wait.

256
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,240
This way.

257
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:25,040
Jiasheng, I couldn't stop Huang Weide.

258
00:14:25,040 --> 00:14:26,680
He rushed upstairs looking for An Ruoxi.

259
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:27,520
Ruoxi.

260
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:28,481
Listen to me.

261
00:14:28,481 --> 00:14:29,961
Go upstairs. It'll be fine.

262
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:31,081
What about you?

263
00:14:31,721 --> 00:14:32,321
It's okay.

264
00:14:32,321 --> 00:14:32,961
Go to bed first.

265
00:14:32,961 --> 00:14:34,121
Wait for me.

266
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:36,640
Be obedient.

267
00:14:37,081 --> 00:14:37,841
Trust me.

268
00:14:52,001 --> 00:14:52,841
Which room?

269
00:14:53,361 --> 00:14:54,241
999, right?

270
00:14:55,241 --> 00:14:56,121
Tu Jiasheng.

271
00:14:56,201 --> 00:14:57,280
Where's your woman?

272
00:14:58,081 --> 00:14:58,961
Tu Jiasheng!

273
00:14:58,961 --> 00:14:59,800
Get out.

274
00:15:00,201 --> 00:15:01,400
Hand her over.

275
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,121
Tu Jiasheng!

276
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:05,920
Mr. Huang.

277
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,440
Weren't the girls good?

278
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,800
Why did you come up?

279
00:15:09,321 --> 00:15:10,560
You've got some nerve.

280
00:15:11,081 --> 00:15:12,040
Tu Jiasheng!

281
00:15:13,121 --> 00:15:14,121
I'm already changed.

282
00:15:14,121 --> 00:15:15,001
Where's she?

283
00:15:15,201 --> 00:15:16,440
- Calm down.
- Where?

284
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,640
Where is she?

285
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:22,081
You think you're hot stuff now?

286
00:15:22,721 --> 00:15:24,121
Daring to mess with me, huh?

287
00:15:24,481 --> 00:15:25,321
Calm down, Mr. Huang.

288
00:15:25,321 --> 00:15:27,160
Calm down?

289
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:28,481
I'll kill you!

290
00:15:28,481 --> 00:15:29,400
You believe it?

291
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:30,481
- Believe it?
- Jiasheng.

292
00:15:30,481 --> 00:15:31,321
Get lost.

293
00:15:31,321 --> 00:15:33,201
Let go! Let go!

294
00:15:33,241 --> 00:15:33,961
Let go!

295
00:15:34,241 --> 00:15:34,784
No!

296
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:37,361
Sweetheart.

297
00:15:37,881 --> 00:15:38,481
Mr. Huang.

298
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:39,640
Mr. Huang.

299
00:15:39,881 --> 00:15:41,201
She's my woman.

300
00:15:41,201 --> 00:15:42,680
- Do me a favor.
- Piss off!

301
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:43,481
Jiasheng!

302
00:15:43,481 --> 00:15:44,680
Come on.

303
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:51,361
Tu Jiasheng!

304
00:15:56,081 --> 00:15:56,721
Let go!

305
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:57,760
Let go of me!

306
00:15:57,760 --> 00:15:58,841
Tu Jiasheng, you see it?

307
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,440
Your woman?

308
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,361
Help!

309
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,160
Here's Deep In The Bustle.

310
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:05,440
Stop playing coy.

311
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,481
Serve me well

312
00:16:07,721 --> 00:16:10,121
and Tu Jiasheng can answer to Nie Feng.

313
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:02,241
Jiasheng.

314
00:17:56,082 --> 00:17:59,756
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

315
00:18:00,055 --> 00:18:03,246
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

316
00:18:05,078 --> 00:18:08,699
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

317
00:18:09,248 --> 00:18:12,047
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

318
00:18:13,518 --> 00:18:17,248
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

319
00:18:17,472 --> 00:18:20,969
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

320
00:18:22,368 --> 00:18:26,055
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

321
00:18:26,693 --> 00:18:31,808
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

322
00:18:32,512 --> 00:18:36,646
♪I feel guilty♪

323
00:18:37,216 --> 00:18:40,960
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

324
00:18:41,824 --> 00:18:45,267
♪Even in tears♪

325
00:18:46,016 --> 00:18:49,930
♪It doesn't matter♪

326
00:18:50,112 --> 00:18:53,935
♪We embrace in dreams♪

327
00:18:54,784 --> 00:18:58,222
♪I let down all my defenses♪

328
00:18:59,456 --> 00:19:02,819
♪Though the story has its end♪

329
00:19:03,584 --> 00:19:11,936
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
